{
  "stem": "26142.8",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And this was the first sign of life that my parents got from us that we are still alive, and we are aiming, trying, to come back.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They told us later that this was a tremendous relief for them, because they heard already what was-- what was happening.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I-- I-- I should digress here for a minute, because I think we left it out.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "The-- I have to-- I have to digress here for one minute, because we are here, Rosh Hashanah, in September.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And the greatest atrocity took place in August 27th and 28th-- three weeks.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I remember, I said before that when we were divided up on the-- on those different kind of trucks, some trucks were dumped off here.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Some trucks were-- those that were dumped off near the city of Kamien Pomorski-- on the-- three weeks later only-- the 27th, the 28th, that was the first-- the first mass-- massacre-- open mass massacre that the Hungarians, together with the Germans, and the Ukrainians, perpetrated around the city of Kamien Pomorski.",
      "word_count": 52
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And over that time, 3/4 of my family perished right there-- three weeks-- only three weeks difference.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I should mention that there were 24,000 people were killed in those two days.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Among them were 16,000 Hungarian refugees. 8,000 local Jews were killed.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it was done completely in an-- on an open.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It wasn't like hidden-- gas-- open-- that the whole-- everybody-- even in Germany, the Polish Jews, that they said that this was a trial.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That the Nazis-- that they wanted to see what the world is going to say.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But the world kept mum-- quiet.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And that happened hours the 27th and the 28th-- three weeks after we were deported from-- from Hungary.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Now we-- I just had to mention that.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
